      <title>泽连斯基称乌克兰寻求恢复与叙利亚的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/ukraine-seeks-to-restore-ties-with-syria-foreign-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亲俄的阿萨德政权垮台后，乌克兰总统派遣高级官员前往叙利亚，试图恢复两国关系。]]></description>
