    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克准备迎接下一波抗议活动，死亡人数不断上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/mozambique-braces-for-next-wave-of-protests-as-death-toll-climbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对党领导人表示，他将对抗议活动的下一阶段作出决定。近三个月前，在有争议的选举之后，抗议活动席卷了这个南部非洲国家，骚乱造成的死亡人数不断上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/mozambique-braces-for-next-wave-of-protests-as-death-toll-climbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:43:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长表示贸易战可能将中国通货紧缩输出至欧洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/ecb-s-knot-says-trade-war-could-export-china-deflation-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员克拉斯·诺特表示，如果美国通过征收新的关税引发贸易战，中国可能开始以折扣价向欧洲出售产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/ecb-s-knot-says-trade-war-could-export-china-deflation-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南宣传力度虽大，生育率仍跌至历史最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/vietnam-birth-rate-slumps-to-record-low-despite-propaganda-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南的生育率已跌至历史最低水平，总和生育率降至每名妇女生育 1.91 个孩子，这是连续第三年降至更替水平以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/vietnam-birth-rate-slumps-to-record-low-despite-propaganda-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 07:39:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
